<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Quiz Master</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
      background-color: #eef7f9;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .container {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 50px;
    }

    .left {
      max-width: 50%;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .logo {
      font-size: 50px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #2e00a3;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .logo .fonts {
      font-size: 40px;
      display: block;
    }

    .title {
      font-size: 30px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-top: 40px;
      color: #1a1a1a;
    }

    .description {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #5a5a89;
      margin-top: 20px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .begin-button {
      background-color: #3d00ff;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      padding: 15px 30px;
      font-size: 18px;
      border-radius: 25px;
      cursor: pointer;
      margin-top: 35px;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .right {
      position: relative;
      width: 50%;
      height: 100vh;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .letters {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
    }

    .letters span {
      position: absolute;
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: hsl(calc(var(--i) * 36), 70%, 50%);
      animation: floatUp 8s linear infinite;
      left: calc(var(--i) * 10%);
      top: 100%;
      transform: rotate(calc(var(--i) * 20deg));
      animation-delay: calc(var(--i) * -0.5s);
    }

    @keyframes floatUp {
      0% {
        transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg);
        opacity: 0;
      }
      20% {
        opacity: 1;
      }
      100% {
        transform: translateY(-120vh) rotate(360deg);
        opacity: 0;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="left">
      <h1 class="logo">Quiz<br><span class="fonts">Master</span></h1>
      <h2 class="title">Do you know your Arial<br>from your Helvetica?</h2>
      <p class="description">
        Weâ€™ve slightly altered the font that appears on 10 famous<br>
        logos and put them next to their legitimate counterparts. Can<br>
        you tell the difference between the bona fides and the<br>
        phoneys?
      </p>
      <a href="/start" class="begin-button">Begin</a>
    </div>
    <div class="right">
      <div class="letters">
        <span style="--i:1;">A</span>
        <span style="--i:2;">B</span>
        <span style="--i:3;">C</span>
        <span style="--i:4;">D</span>
        <span style="--i:5;">E</span>
        <span style="--i:6;">F</span>
        <span style="--i:7;">G</span>
        <span style="--i:8;">H</span>
        <span style="--i:9;">I</span>
        <span style="--i:10;">J</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
